==Youth One-Day International captains==

This is a list of cricketers who have [[captain (cricket)|captained]] the [[Bangladeshi Under-19 cricket team]] for at least one Under-19 [[One Day International]]. The table of results is complete to the third Under-19 ODI against [[English cricket team|England]] in 2004. Bangladesh's greatest success in the Under-19 World Cup has been winning the plate, which is the competition for teams failing to progress past the first qualifying round of the Under-19 World Cup. They achieved this in both 1997/8 and 2003/4, and during the latter tournament, beat [[Australian cricket team|Australia]] in doing so.

